<!ENTITY % cxml.requests "(ConfirmationRequest |
                           ShipNoticeRequest |
                           ServiceEntryRequest |
                           CopyRequest |
                           SalesOrderRequest |
			   TimeCardInfoRequest |
			   ReceiptRequest |
               OrderStatusRequest |
